Advantages and Disadvantages of Using Social Media in Our Daily life and Society .
Nowadays , with the development of technology and society , social media begin more popular and even person in our daily life .
We communicate with others using social media , such as twitters , facebooks and microblog more and more frequently .
There is no need to for people to go out of their home to interact with others , was chat by , share pictures , tell others what they have done or funny stories .
It seems that people build a good relationship with others having the thus media , but the problems come out .
Pepopes do not know how to talk with others face to confront , especially the strangers .
Then , we need to talk about the advantages and disadvantages of using social media in your diary is and society .
As for the advantages , there are two aspects : nowadays convenient to contact others , more to know about others .
One advantage is that it is more convenience to touch others by social media such
In early days , if one wants to tell some important news to another A , which lives far away , he needs to write letters and it wastes time .
The long distance and time-consuming make spreading kind messages quite difficult at that time .
Therefore , people may not contact with the faraway friends and relatives unless there are something important .
However , people now can contact with anyone all over the world who can use computer at any time , and there is no time delay of messages .
The other advantage is that it is easier to learn about others which social media .
If there just no social media , it is difficult for people to be about a stranger .
They may collect information about that person by asking his guys , colleagues o family members .
end the information collected may not be intact which true .
Unlike today , with the help with social media , people can easily get the information they want just by searching on line , and know about what this person did everyday at what days .
As for the disadvantages of social media in our daily life , wasting time , causing illness related to sitting long time ago the computer , quick-spread of rumor and fake news , mostly importantly , making people lost the ability to talk to others face to face confidently .
It is weird that people sit around the table family all wall to their phones and do not talk with each other .
