No matter it is a party , dinner or just simply get-together , there always are some people bow their head and playing their phones even is family and them are in front of them .
In a conclusion , there are both advantage and disadvantages life using social media in daily life .
People should enjoy the advantages of social media while be careful of the disadvantages of that and try their best to avoid the disadvantages be to them and their friends and family .
